{"tid":1504694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地可唔可以自己開返個reddit咁既英文國際論壇","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T18:56:58.000Z","uid":302475,"like":216,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"7806aad17f065c85c4428f694295d341aa65434d","tid":1504694,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"望到Twitter連仔acc成日用中文post，要有人譯返做英文，突然有呢個諗法<br />\n用返連仔差不多架構就得，如果加返熱門置頂post功能，總之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好用過reddit就得</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nReddit一黎有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中資</span></span>，二黎網頁設計真係唔係咁易睇同用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣可以多個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>宣傳溝通平台</strong></span></span>，集中外國討論，外國記者又可以直接開post訪問，有咩呢邊<span style=\"color: orange;\">中文突發/熱門</span>都可以放係個邊一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係Twitter開個英文acc可以用埋<span style=\"color: orange;\">腦魔</span>做張漫畫宣傳又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n能人異士好多，我信香港可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>自己搭返個熱門國際論壇</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e89029ba76a619abe7046939668c9b7b783d813","tid":1504694,"uid":4574,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"用twitter 做文宣"},{"pid":"5